reviews.text: One of my favourite coffee shop liver kuey teow! Not over cooked so its really soft & juicy, prepare for long queues during lunch time! Then only thing I don’t like about this place is my reception is terrible, can’t even receive or send out whatsapp messages

Famous Tanglin Crispy Curry Puff available at Ubi! Freshly prepared on premise. $2 per curry puff.

Flavourful filling with generous potato, egg and chicken. Skin is flaky and not oily.

Tried their Sardine Puff too, generous sardine with tangy onions.
Nov'24. Nice food available. Cozy, Aircon eating local eating place at industrial park, price might be slightly higher than nearby coffee shop but worth escaping the heat
A cosy place situated in the industrial area. There are different stalls in the food court. Tried the Thai food there. Tom Yum and Basil Pork Rice. Both tasted ok. The ambience was good.

The food court is located in a light industrial area and primarily serves the office workers in the vicinity. It operates only during weekdays and working hours. When we visited in the evening, only a Thai food stall and a Western food stall were still opened. We tried several dishes from the Thai food stall and found them to be authentic and reasonably priced. We recommend this hidden gem to anyone looking for a delicious and affordable meal in the area.
